{"tid":1257173,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《遍地開花》將軍澳黑警打人放映會","createTime":"2019-06-25T12:00:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T15:08:02.000Z","uid":176405,"like":64,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"4ff37027d3c1d8c6975876327ed637cd831316db","tid":1257173,"uid":176405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T12:00:28.000Z","msg":"今晚星期二可以又搞活動<br />\n「黑警打人放映會」<br />\n同時會派埋埋單張<br />\n<br />\n今次地點：將軍澳地鐵站A出口位置等<br />\n時間：20:00左右開始<br />\n<br />\n大量需要人力幫手派單張<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n辛苦晒，辛苦晒<br />\n香港人，6月哩一場係戰役，唔係一兩場可以定勝負。<br />\n我地仲未贏㗎，因為民意逆轉緊，藍營開始有影片同文宣攻勢；但我地都仲未輸，因為我地仲有人堅信緊自己嘅信念同守護緊嘅意義<br />\n<br />\n收到哩個信息可能係00後，90後，80後可能係我嘅親人<br />\n我地每個人堅守，堅信嘅都唔同，價值觀都唔同，但正正因為我地係香港人我地先可以擁有唔同嘅價值觀同堅信嘅事情，不致於被統一思想。<br />\n天與地一句說話好重要<br />\n「和諧唔係一百個人講同一句說話，和諧係一百個人有唔同說話之餘，而又互相尊重。」<br />\n<br />\n香港人共勉之<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8126505ff944092faa66406d3aa21d7993a52913","tid":1257173,"uid":52023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T12:02:25.000Z","msg":"g持"},{"pid":"9e6bbc686f2fd4483f762c63b6a460fbc828eef4","tid":1257173,"uid":176405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T12:03:04.000Z","msg":"咁遲先開Po Sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dccc7ccf31bd42b72041d5f4016ed4460572efe","tid":1257173,"uid":217185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T12:03:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b822a8cdbc9489a3b